scene.message:
Maki: You idiot!!{nl}
Why did you kill Papa?!{nl}
Do you know what you've done?!{waitkey}Waaaaaaaaaaaah!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: It's a lie...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
That this is me...{waitkey}{nl}
That I'm the one who{nl}
hurt everyone...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: The real me killed{nl}
the person she leaned on{nl}
with her own hands?!{waitkey}{clearbox}No one will save us{nl}
anymore!{nl}
It's all over!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Three... Makis...{nl}
Jesus... how can this be...{nl}
They're all Maki...{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: They're all the{nl}
same Sonomura?{nl}
For real?... No way...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Don't come...{nl}
Don't look at me!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Calm down, Sonomura!{nl}
It's gotta be some{nl}
mistake... right?{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No, no, no! It's true!{nl}
This is me!{nl}
I just know it!{waitkey}{clearbox}Twisting the city,{nl}
hurting everyone -{nl}
it was all me! It was me!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Calm down, Maki!{nl}
You were only being used...{nl}
Don't blame yourself, okay?{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Calm down!{nl}
You were just used, yeah?{nl}
Come over here, quick.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Sonomura!{nl}
Don't sweat it!{nl}
Kandori's the bad guy!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Please, don't be{nl}
kind to me...{wait_fr:88} I understand{nl}
it all now...{nl}
I was jealous of everyone...{waitkey}{clearbox}Walking the town in cute{nl}
clothes, swooning over boys,{nl}
laughing out loud...{waitkey}{clearbox}I envied everyone heading{nl}
happily off to school...{waitkey}'Just let the school and town{nl}
vanish'...{waitkey}I thought that...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I wanted to do{nl}
something but I couldn't...{nl}
I cried and cried...{waitkey}{clearbox}Envying people, resenting{nl}
them... building an ideal{nl}
town and self for comfort...{waitkey}{clearbox}You see now, don't you?{wait_fr:88}{nl}
I'm... a hopeless girl.{waitkey}I have no right to live!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: You too...{nl}
it's over for you now.{nl}
Kandori's gone already.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Now once more...{nl}
we can return to a{nl}
quiet town...{waitkey}Thank you, big brother.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: You still...{nl}
mean to keep living{nl}
in that town?!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yes...{nl}
because if I don't,{nl}
I'll be so pitiful...{waitkey}{clearbox}You'll come back too.{nl}
I want you to keep up{nl}
the ideal me.{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: No!{nl}
I never want to go back{nl}
to that town!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: So now you've come{nl}
to like big brother...{nl}
Fine, I'll bring out as many{nl}
as you like.{waitkey}{clearbox}It's such an easy thing...{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Bye-bye{wait_fr:60}, big brother...{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: Yes, everything ends!{nl}
Everyone should just vanish!{nl}
Everyone, disappeaaar!!{waitkey}{ret}

Maki: I... I can't stay{nl}
by everyone's side{nl}
anymore...{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: ...{wait_fr:88}You...{wait_fr:88} you idiot!!{nl}
Why... why is this{nl}
happening?!{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: {ctl0f:1}!{nl}
Let's go back into{nl}
Sonomura's heart!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...Wait, Inaba.{wait_fr:88}{nl}
Do you know the foolish{nl}
woman called Pandora?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: A legendary woman who{nl}
opened the gods' box and{nl}
loosed every evil on earth...{waitkey}{clearbox}Sonomura is, in a sense,{nl}
Pandora. The city's ruin{nl}
is what she wished for.{waitkey}Rather than save such a{nl}
woman, destroying the Deva{nl}
System must come first.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Wh-why you...{nl}
And you call yourself{nl}
a friend?!{waitkey}If we smash that thing,{nl}
what happens to Sonomura?!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: As far as I can tell,{nl}
Sonomura's life is sustained{nl}
by that system...{waitkey}{clearbox}Destroy it and she'll{nl}
likely die too. But while{nl}
it stands, nothing's solved.{waitkey}{clearbox}Don't put personal feelings{nl}
first... Sacrifice the few{nl}
to save the many...{waitkey}It's the obvious choice.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: I misjudged you...{nl}
Honestly, I never figured{nl}
you for that cold a bastard...{waitkey}{clearbox}Sure, maybe you're right.{nl}
It's grown-up logic.{nl}
But still...{waitkey}{clearbox}If Sonomura's the one who{nl}
hurt us, she's also the one{nl}
who tried to save us all!{waitkey}{clearbox}I believe in Sonomura's heart.{nl}
She'll cut ties with that{nl}
machine for sure.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Yes...{nl}
We have to show Maki{nl}
she's not alone.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Well said...{nl}
If it helps Maki rise{nl}
above herself,{waitkey}then I'm going.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase's going too...{nl}
I still have her{nl}
handkerchief...{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: I'm going...{nl}
If that white kid is{nl}
Sonomura too,{waitkey}I owe her for taking me in.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph...{nl}
Trust the heart, is it...{nl}
Yamaoka said he believed{nl}
in my heart too...{waitkey}{clearbox}In the end, people are{nl}
creatures of feeling.{nl}
Logic aside, it's the heart{nl}
that speaks last...{waitkey}I'll go too.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Geez, always splitting{nl}
hairs. Why not just say{nl}
so plainly...{waitkey}{clearbox}Aren't you the smart grown-up{nl}
who's gonna stay behind?{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Unfortunately, I'm 17.{nl}
By law, I'm not yet{nl}
recognized as an adult.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: Heh...{nl}
You never run out of{nl}
comebacks, do you.{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: {ctl0f:1}, no time{nl}
like the present. Let's use{nl}
the Deva System to return{nl}
into Sonomura's heart.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: H-hey!?{nl}
Something's showing{nl}
in the mirror!{waitkey}{ret}
